---
title: Cheesy Double Mustard Chicken Risotto with Leek & Lemon
description: A hearty baked risotto is exactly what we’re craving when the cooler weather hits, and this might be our favourite flavour combo yet.Chicken is browned and then slowly cooked in the risotto for ultimate tenderness. Leek and soffritto mix add subtle sweetness, while dijon mustard packs a punch with flavour and lends the dish an irresistible golden hue. Dig in!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6687933a98a5211d32d1d081-260f3950.jpeg
